Also called the Queen of the Invisible Art, the Axe Princess of Conquest, and the Daul of Laduguer, Deep Duerra is&nbsp;the duergar goddess of psionics, conquest, expansion, duergar warriors, and duergar psionicists. She is said to be the daughter of Laduguer.
She has a Realm seperate from her father's in Thuldanin, the second Layer of Acheron, called the Citadel of Thought. She appears as a powerful gray dwarf in ornate chain mail, carrying a battle axe, her only hair a monk's tonsured cut and a tightly wound braid. 

